<subSubSection lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="532" pageId="1" pageNumber="530" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="1.[828,1436,1894,2077]" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[828,984,1894,1917]" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Distribution.</emphasis>
An uncommon but widely distributed species, characteristic of beech forests. It is known from several European countries (
<collectingCountry box="[1156,1312,1958,1981]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Great Britain</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1326,1431,1958,1981]" name="Denmark" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Denmark</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[828,910,1990,2013]" name="Austria" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Austria</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[924,1055,1990,2013]" name="Switzerland" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Switzerland</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1069,1157,1990,2013]" name="Sweden" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Sweden</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1171,1245,1990,2013]" name="Russia" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Russia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1260,1349,1990,2013]" name="Ukraine" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry name="Bulgaria" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Bulgaria</collectingCountry>
), including the Czech and Slovak Republics (
<bibRefCitation author="HELLER K. &amp; MENZEL F." pageId="1" pageNumber="530" refId="ref4307" refString="HELLER K. &amp; MENZEL F. 2017: Fauna Europaea: Sciaridae. In: BEUK P. &amp; PAPE T: Fauna Europaea: Diptera. Fauna Europaea version 2017.06, https: // fauna-eu. org. Accessed 27. xii. 2018." type="url" year="2017">HELLER &amp; MENZEL 2017</bibRefCitation>
). New record for 
<collectingCountry box="[1190,1290,2054,2077]" name="Czech Republic" pageId="1" pageNumber="530">Bohemia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340496" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5340496" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5340496/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="531" startId="2.[151,188,2036,2055]" targetBox="[227,1360,200,1983]" targetPageId="2">
